{"type":"message","id":"e79a69bf","parentId":"e79e40dd","timestamp":"2026-03-30T01:41:32.318Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The fetch didn't get the full content. Let me try to get more details about Feishu's status indicators. Based on what I know and searched:\n\n飞书的用户状态圆点颜色含义:\n\n1. **绿点** - 在线，表示对方正在使用飞书\n2. **灰点** - 不在线，离线状态\n3. **红点** - 这可能不是状态，而是消息未读数或者其他通知\n4. **蓝点** - 这个不太确定，可能是某种特殊状态\n\n实际上飞书的状态系统比较简单：\n- 默认没有特殊状态就是默认头像\n- 可以设置个人状态（如\"忙碌\"、\"请假\"等）\n\n让我再搜索一下确认具体颜色含义。\n","thinkingSignature":"d90a89dad0fa66d7b9128f4261a0962b7f2d2cf952accf0dcf03e84a6ab00a27"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yzt0l0nk7edj_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":5,"query":"飞书 绿点 灰点 在线状态 头像旁边小圆点 含义"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":563,"output":193,"cacheRead":24512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25268,"cost":{"input":0.00016889999999999999,"output":0.0002316,"cacheRead":0.0007353599999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0011358599999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774834887469,"responseId":"061907c7b27abfd145d500f4a47a0e0e"}}
