=\"03a89cb4068c22b8\">>>","siteName":"www.feishu.cn"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"424cea0e689f249d\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n一文完全搞懂OpenClaw（Clawdbot）附飞书对接教程！ - 飞书官网\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"424cea0e689f249d\">>>","url":"https://www.feishu.cn/content/article/7602519239445974205","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"7daa1fe6dd89264f\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n阅读时间：18分钟 · 字节跳动旗下 AI 工作平台\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"7daa1fe6dd89264f\">>>","siteName":"www.feishu.cn"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"d2c1842327a4ebe6\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n飞书帮助中心 - 飞书使用技巧及常见问题解答\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"d2c1842327a4ebe6\">>>","url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5ea0c02c07420715\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThe Feishu Help Center provides FAQs for enterprise administrators and members who use Feishu collaborative software. These FAQs cover topics such as registration, login, OKRs, remote working, smart attendance, and audio and video conferencing.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5ea0c02c07420715\">>>","siteName":"www.feishu.cn"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774834901312}}
{"type":"message","id":"e6e278e0","parentId":"e639f77a","timestamp":"2026-03-30T01:41:48.037Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Based on my research, I can provide an answer about Feishu's user status indicators. Let me summarize what I found.\n","thinkingSignature":"29c0ae6d26879c1341483b45db1631c4cd6676ce6173ff85cfd74e785de2e763"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n[[reply_to_current]] 🦊 帮你查了一下，飞书用户头像旁边的小圆点状态含义如下：\n\n## 飞书在线状态指示器\n\n| 颜色 | 状态含义 |\n|------|----------|\n| 🟢 **绿色** | 在线（当前正在使用飞书） |\n| 🟡 **黄色/橙色** | 暂时离开/离开（短暂不操作或设置了离开状态） |\n| 🔴 **灰色** | 离线（未使用飞书或不显示状态） |\n\n## 关于你说的\"红点\"\n\n飞书里可能有几种红点：\n\n**1. 消息未读红点** ⬆️\n- 消息列表、对话、文档右上角的红色数字角标\n- 代表有新消息/新内容未读\n\n**2. 系统通知红点** ⚠️\n- 有人在 @你 或回复你\n- 有审批/待办任务\n\n**3. 头像旁的在线状态**\n- 飞书的在线状态主要是绿色/灰色\n- 红色一般不是状态，而是\"未读\"提醒\n\n---\n\n简单说：\n- **绿点** = 对方在线，可以秒回\n- **灰点** = 对方离线或不在线\n- **红点/数字角标** = 你有未读消息或待处理事项\n\n你看到的是哪种情况？是头像旁边的状态点，还是消息上的角标？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1512,"output":317,"cacheRead":25024,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26853,"cost":{"input":0.00045359999999999997,"output":0.0003804,"cacheRead":0.00075072,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00158472}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774834901317,"responseId":"061907d588f0abc071c17dfb0df0a3c7"}}
